OL,5,G1900 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FBelgium v Iran (Kick-off 8.00pm).
OL,7,     FGroup G continues at Los Angeles
OL,8,     FStadium in Inglewood, USA, where
OL,9,     Fthe sides face each other for the
OL,10,     Ffirst time in their history. Some
OL,11,     Fof the Iranian players may be
OL,12,     Ffamiliar to fans of England and
OL,13,     FWales, having been drawn in the
OL,14,     Fsame group four years ago in
OL,15,     FQatar, with mixed results. A 6-2
OL,16,     Fdrubbing at the hands of England
OL,17,     Fwas followed by a 2-0 win against
OL,18,     FWales, with both goals coming deep
OL,19,     Finto injury time. They'll start as
OL,20,     Funderdogs here against Belgium,
OL,21,     Fwhose manager Rudi Garcia is
OL,22,     Fleading them for the first time in
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
