OL,5,G2235 ITV News and Weather
OL,6,     FRound-up of the latest headlines
OL,7,G2249 STV Weather North
OL,8,G2250 The Essex Millionaire Murders
OL,9,     FA look at the investigation into
OL,10,     Fthe murders of Carol and Stephen
OL,11,     FBaxter, a wealthy couple in their
OL,12,     F60s who were found dead by their
OL,13,     Fdaughter on Easter Sunday in 2023
OL,14,     Fin Essex
OL,15,G2345 TikTok: Murder Gone Viral
OL,16,     FAfter surviving an attempt on her
OL,17,     Flife, TikTok star Sania Khan went
OL,18,     Fviral campaigning for South Asian
OL,19,     FwomenOCGOs rights. Little did she
OL,20,     Frealise this would put her in
OL,21,     Fmortal danger from her ex-husband.
