OL,5,G0130 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FNew Zealand v Egypt (Kick-off
OL,7,     F2.00am). Semra Hunter presents
OL,8,     Fcoverage of the second Group G
OL,9,     Fmatch for both sides, which takes
OL,10,     Fplace at BC Place Vancouver in
OL,11,     FCanada. New Zealand had yet to win
OL,12,     Fa fixture at a World Cup finals in
OL,13,     Ftheir previous attempts in 1982
OL,14,     Fand 2010 but, in part due to the
OL,15,     Fhuge number of teams now taking
OL,16,     Fpart, they were afforded one of
OL,17,     Fthe most comfortable paths to
OL,18,     Fqualification of all nations. They
OL,19,     Fdefeated Tahiti, Samoa and Vanuatu
OL,20,     Fin the group stage of the Oceania
OL,21,     Fsection, and followed that with
OL,22,     Fknockout victories against Fiji
